snippet.title: Jet Lancer Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Jet Lancer is coming to PC and Mac.

Wishlist on Steam: http://armor.ag/JetLancer

📣 Community 📣
Homepage: http://www.jetlancergame.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/JetLancerGame
Discord: https://discord.gg/945Vu2U

Jet Lancer is a frenetic aerial dog-fighting game where you hunt enemy pilots, carve up giant robots, and defy death at supersonic speeds as a daring mercenary in the far future.
